General.Name: NP3 Fastigheter AB (publ)
General.Description: NP3 Fastigheter AB (publ), a real estate company, rents commercial real properties. Its real estate portfolio consists of commercial, industrial, logistics, office, and other properties, which include housing, restaurants, storage rooms, and gym, as well as hotels and community properties, such as schools located in Sundsvall, Gävle, Dalarna, Östersund, Umeå, Skellefteå, Luleå, and Central Sweden. The company was founded in 2007 and is headquartered in Sundsvall, Sweden.
